Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,寄身在屍花之王 泰坦．阿爾姆上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.04,0:00:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1145.333,970)}Titan Arum
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,這可不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼大量的魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不斷地被吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,精靈...
